headline: EQT Corporation (EQT) Hits High-End Sales Volumes, Cites Strong Well Productivity and Synergies
summary: EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) ranks among the stocks to benefit from an onshoring boom. In the second quarter of 2025, EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) reported adjusted earnings per share of $0.45, higher than the consensus estimate of $0.42 and above analyst expectations. Revenue also jumped to $2.56 billion, significantly more than the $1.76 billion analysts had predicted. […]
